name: Saturn in Orbit
description:
Travel through space to visit the Sixth planet from our sun, Saturn. The Planet is a gas giant, made up of mostly helium and hydrogen. The iconic rings around Saturn are composed of tiny particles that orbit around the planet.

This piece was created using the Javascript library, p5.js, and features some slight interactivity. The piece breaks free from the laws of physics and gravity and allows the viewer to interact with the planet. Move your cursor around the canvas to interact with the piece.
